Title: Prometheus (1)
Plot:
A news reporter threatens to expose a top-secret military project, but when Carter and Jonas
give her a tour of the X-303, they discover that she is a pawn in a much larger plot.
GuestStars: Colby Johannson, Todd Hann, Kyle Cassie, Catherine Lough Haggquist, Jason Gaffney, Bill Marchant, Enid-Raye Adams, Ian Tracey, George Wyner, Kendall Cross, John de Lancie
